    "id": "v4"
  }, "v4"), mdx("p", null, "Nhi\u1EC1u l\u1EA7n ta sai c\xE1c t\xF4i t\u1EDB ta, t\u1EE9c c\xE1c nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri \u0111\u1EBFn v\u1EDBi c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i. Ta ph\xE1n qua h\u1ECD r\u1EB1ng, 'Ch\u1EDB l\xE0m \u0111i\u1EC1u gh\xEA t\u1EDFm n\u1EA7y m\xE0 ta gh\xE9t.' "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v5"
  }, "v5"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng ch\xFAng kh\xF4ng nghe c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng th\xE8m \u0111\u1EC3 \xFD \u0111\u1EBFn. Ch\xFAng v\u1EABn c\u1EE9 l\xE0m \xE1c v\xE0 d\xE2ng h\u01B0\u01A1ng cho c\xE1c th\u1EA7n kh\xE1c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v6"
  }, "v6"), mdx("p", null, "Cho n\xEAn ta t\u1ECF c\u01A1n th\u1ECBnh n\u1ED9 ta tr\xEAn ch\xFAng. Ta tr\xFAt c\u01A1n gi\u1EADn ta tr\xEAn c\xE1c th\u1ECB tr\u1EA5n Giu-\u0111a v\xE0 c\xE1c \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng ph\u1ED1 Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem \u0111\u1EC3 nh\u1EEFng n\u01A1i \u0111\xF3 th\xE0nh ch\u1ED7 \u0111\u1ED5 n\xE1t v\xE0 \u0111\u1ED1ng \u0111\xE1 v\u1EE5n cho \u0111\u1EBFn h\xF4m nay.\" "), mdx("h6", {
