    "id": "v29"
  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA ph\xE1n, \"Ta s\u1EBD cho c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i m\u1ED9t d\u1EA5u hi\u1EC7u \u0111\u1EC3 th\u1EA5y ta s\u1EBD tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u1EDF \u0111\xE2y t\u1EA1i Ai-c\u1EADp. Khi c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i th\u1EA5y d\u1EA5u hi\u1EC7u \u0111\xF3 th\xEC s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFt nh\u1EEFng l\u1EDDi ta ngh\u1ECBch l\u1EA1i c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i ch\u1EAFc ch\u1EAFn s\u1EBD th\xE0nh s\u1EF1 th\u1EADt.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v30"
  }, "v30"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA ph\xE1n: \"H\xF3p-ra, vua Ai-c\u1EADp hi\u1EC7n c\xF3 nh\u1EEFng k\u1EBB th\xF9 mu\u1ED1n gi\u1EBFt n\xF3. Ta s\u1EAFp trao n\xF3 v\xE0o tay c\xE1c k\u1EBB th\xF9 n\xF3 nh\u01B0 ta \u0111\xE3 trao X\xEA-\u0111\xEA-kia, vua Giu-\u0111a v\xE0o tay N\xEA-bu-c\xE1t-n\u1EBFt-xa, vua Ba-by-l\xF4n, l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi mu\u1ED1n gi\u1EBFt n\xF3.\""), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
